Qc2 { Avoiding the potential Ne4-fork. } 11... c5
{ White's queen feels uncomfortable on the c-file now. We want to take on d4 and then exploit the pin on the c-file with d5. }
12. Rd1 { Pepraring to take on d4 with the rook. } 12... cxd4 13. Rxd4 Qe7
