Rbxc1 cxd4 18. cxd4 Rc8
{ I like Black's chances here because of the better pawn structure @@StartBracket@@the d4-pawn is a potential target@@EndBracket@@ and the strong knight on d5. All endgames would also be in Black's favour, as the pawn majority on the queenside can expand, while White's pawn majority is not flexible at the moment. }
