12. Rfd1
{ White occupies the open file, hoping it will help solve their d4-square issues. }
12... Bxf3 13. Bxf3
{ Now Black has to bring one of the knights to d4 - one possible route is via a6-c5-e6-d4. }
13... Na6
{ It is clear that White's bishop is a bad piece. Not only is it passive but it also can't participate in the fight for the d4-square. }
