11. O-O Nf4 12. Bc2 Bg4
{ We forced White's bishop to retreat to c2, a bad place for it because it's more difficult to prepare c5 with Rc1 or Qc2. As for Black's plan, we should finish our development by bringing the knight on b8 to either a6 or d7 and then prepare f5. }
