d5 10. e3
{ It makes no sense for White to take on d5, as it would free our 'bad' bishop. }
10... dxc4
{ An extra pawn should justify our difficulty in finding a way for the c8-bishop to enter the game!  11.Qxe4  doesn't work because of  11...Qxb2  with the rook on a1 falling. }
