8. Nc3 a4 9. d5 { White wants to get as much space in the center as possible. }
9... Nb4 10. bxa4
{ The extra pawn is doubled, thus it can't even be felt, while the early over expansion in the center will give White some headaches. }
10... exd5 11. cxd5 Ne4
