{ The alternative to  6...Nc6  . Black goes for the typical setup with O-O and e5. }
7. Nc3 O-O 8. Bg2
{ White does their best to finish their development as fast as possible. } 8...
e5 { We need to open up our bishop! } 9. O-O Re8
{ Preparing e4 followed by e3. White needs to decide what to do about the pawn structure in the center. There are quite a few options... }
